snippet.title: Cat Quest II - Steam Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cat Quest II is a fast paced open world action RPG where you play as both a cat and a dog. Explore a massive world filled with monsters, dungeons and quests, as you strive to bring peace back to your kingdoms during a time of war! 

The game releases later this year on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One, and on 24th September on PC/Steam!

Add to your wishlist now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/914710/Cat_Quest_II/

https://pqube.co.uk/cat-quest-2/

Check out #CatQuestII and @TheGentlebros on social media and Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/catquest

PQube Discord server! https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU
